'''Confederación Empresarial de Sociedades Laborales de España''' ('''CONFESAL''') is a [[Spain|Spanish]] enterprise organization whose objectives are the representation and defense of the interests of companies in [[labor union|labor societies]] in Spain. CONFESAL formed on 4 July 1987.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=afh0QNvA9OUC&pg=PA73&dq=Confederaci%C3%B3n+Empresarial+de+Sociedades+Laborales+de+Espa%C3%B1a+1987&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi-6cuB04vXAhWQbFAKHSXcAH4Q6AEIKzAA#v=onepage&q=Confederaci%C3%B3n%20Empresarial%20de%20Sociedades%20Laborales%20de%20Espa%C3%B1a%201987&f=false|title=Diccionario de Economia Social, Volume 6|publisher=Ecobook - Editorial Del Economista |date=December 2009|language=Spanish}}</ref>

