==Business career== After retiring as a player, he completed his studies industrial engineering at the [[Latin American University of Science and Technology]]. He is currently General Director for Central America at [[Gruma]] (Grupo Maseca), a food production company.<ref name=Prensa>[http://www.laprensa.hn/lasultimas24/703626-97/de-las-canchas-de-f%C3%BAtbol-a-la-presidencia-de-gruma-ca De las canchas de fútbol a la presidencia de GRUMA CA] - La Prensa {{es|icon}}</ref>
